'''Killzone: Shadow Fall''' is an upcoming video game by [[Guerrilla Games]] for the [[Playstation 4]] console. It will be the fourth game in the [[Killzone (series)|Killzone]] video game series.<ref>http://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2013/02/20/killzone-shadowfall-announced-for-ps4/</ref><ref>http://venturebeat.com/2013/02/20/sony-unveils-killzone-shadow-fall-for-the-playstation-4/</ref>

==Plot==
''Killzone: Shadow Fall'' will be set around 30 years after the events of the previous Killzone games. The game features the Vektan and Helghast factions living in a large city that is divided by a security wall.<ref>http://www.denofgeek.com/games/24554/killzone-shadow-fall-trailer</ref> The Helghast are fighting for their right to exist, while the Vektans are fighting for survival.<ref>http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/122267-The-Helghast-Come-Knocking-in-PS4s-Killzone-Shadow-Fall</ref>

==Release==
''Killzone: Shadow Fall'' was announced at the ''PlayStation Meeting'' in February 2013, and will be a Playstation 4 [[launch title]].<ref>http://www.polygon.com/2013/2/20/4005462/killzone-4-ps4-reveal-trailer</ref>

